{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893008505,"sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","part":{"id":"prt_d7b78c8bf001j71JDmHtQJ9fyr","messageID":"msg_d7b78b9a2001VtshnlnNcV94uQ","sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-aaa3fe7b3b6b4a589ed61acc7a0294e2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 平台生成基于 Kubernetes client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供对自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）的强类型 API 访问能力，支持 CRUD 操作、Watch 机制和 Informer 模式。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: client-go 类型客户端是 AgentCube 平台开发者工具链的核心组成部分，旨在：\n10: \n11: 1. **类型安全** - 提供编译时类型检查，避免运行时错误\n12: 2. **开发效率** - 简化 Kubernetes API 调用，提供简洁的开发体验\n13: 3. **标准化接口** - 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 最佳实践和约定\n14: 4. **高性能** - 支持高效的 Watch 和 Informer 机制\n15: 5. **可维护性** - 自动生成客户端代码，与 CRD 定义保持同步\n16: \n17: ## Module\n18: \n19: `client-go` - Go 客户端库\n20: \n21: ## Language\n22: \n23: Go\n24: \n25: ## Size\n26: \n27: L\n28: \n29: ## Scope\n30: \n31: ### In Scope\n32: \n33: 1. **ClientSet 生成**\n34:    - AgentRuntime client\n35:    - CodeInterpreter client\n36:    - 支持所有 Kubernetes API verbs (get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete)\n37: \n38: 2. **Typed Client**\n39:    - Namespace-scoped operations\n40:    - Cluster-scoped operations (如需要)\n41:    - 支持子资源 (status, scale)\n42: \n43: 3. **Informer 集成**\n44:    - AgentRuntime informer\n45:    - CodeInterpreter informer\n46:    - 事件处理器支持\n47:    - 缓存机制\n48: \n49: 4. **Lister 支持**\n50:    - AgentRuntime lister\n51:    - CodeInterpreter lister\n52:    - 高效的只读访问\n53: \n54: 5. **代码生成工具**\n55:    - code-generator 配置\n56:    - 自定义代码生成脚本\n57:    - 自动化文档生成\n58: \n59: ### Out of Scope\n60: \n61: - 其他语言的客户端（Python、Java 等）\n62: - 跨平台的客户端生成\n63: - gRPC 客户端生成\n64: - REST API 直接调用封装\n65: - CLI 工具集成\n66: \n67: ## Impact Analysis\n68: \n69: ### Components Impacted\n70: \n71: 1. **Controller Manager**\n72:    - 需要使用生成的客户端管理 AgentRuntime\n73:    - 需要 Informer 监听资源变更\n74: \n75: 2. **Workload Manager**\n76:    - 需要使用生成的客户端创建和管理 AgentRuntime\n77:    - 需要访问 AgentRuntime status\n78: \n79: 3. **外部工具和脚本**\n80:    - 需要使用客户端进行资源操作\n81:    - 需要 Watch 机制监听资源事件\n82: \n83: ### Dependencies\n84: \n85: - **Go 1.19+**: 客户端库开发语言\n86: - **Kubernetes 1.20+**: API 兼容性\n87: - **k8s.io/code-generator**: 代码生成工具\n88: - **k8s.io/client-go**: Kubernetes 客户端库基础\n89: \n90: ### Breaking Changes\n91: \n92: 无破坏性变更。客户端库是新增的 Go 模块。\n93: \n94: ## Design Decisions\n95: \n96: ### 使用 code-generator 生成客户端\n97: \n98: **选择**: 使用 Kubernetes 官方的 code-generator 工具\n99: \n100: **理由**:\n101: - 官方维护，稳定可靠\n102: - 与 Kubernetes API 版本同步\n103: - 支持所有 Kubernetes API 特性\n104: - 广泛使用，社区成熟\n105: \n106: **示例**:\n107: ```bash\n108: go run k8s.io/code-generator/cmd/client-gen \\\n109:   --input-base=\"github.com/agentcube/apis\" \\\n110:   --input=\"runtime/v1alpha1\" \\\n111:   --clientset-path=\"github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client\"\n112: ```\n113: \n114: ### 包结构组织\n115: \n116: **选择**: 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 标准包结构\n117: \n118: **理由**:\n119: - 与 Kubernetes 生态保持一致\n120: - 便于开发者理解和使用\n121: - 支持未来扩展\n122: \n123: **包结构**:\n124: ```\n125: client-go/\n126: ├── pkg/\n127: │   ├── apis/\n128: │   │   └── runtime/\n129: │   │       └── v1alpha1/\n130: │   │           ├── doc.go\n131: │   │           ├── register.go\n132: │   │           ├── types.go\n133: │   │           ├── agentruntime_types.go\n134: │   │           └── codeinterpreter_types.go\n135: │   ├── client/\n136: │   │   ├── clientset/\n137: │   │   │   └── versioned/\n138: │   │   │       ├── clientset.go\n139: │   │   │       ├── doc.go\n140: │   │   │       ├── fake/\n141: │   │   │       └── typed/\n142: │   │   │           └── runtime/\n143: │   │   │               └── v1alpha1/\n144: │   │   │                   ├── agentruntime.go\n145: │   │   │                   ├── codeinterpreter.go\n146: │   │   │                   ├── fake/\n147: │   │   │                   │   ├── agentruntime.go\n148: │   │   │                   │   └── codeinterpreter.go\n149: │   │   │                   ├── generated_expansion.go\n150: │   │   │                   └── runtime_client.go\n151: │   ├── informers/\n152: │   │   └── externalversions/\n153: │   │       ├── internalinterfaces/\n154: │   │       └── runtime/\n155: │   │           └── v1alpha1/\n156: │   │               ├── agentruntime.go\n157: │   │               ├── codeinterpreter.go\n158: │   │               └── interface.go\n159: │   └── listers/\n160: │       └── runtime/\n161: │           └── v1alpha1/\n162: │               ├── agentruntime.go\n163: │               └── codeinterpreter.go\n164: ├── go.mod\n165: ├── go.sum\n166: ├── Makefile\n167: └── README.md\n168: ```\n169: \n170: ### API Group 和 Version 命名\n171: \n172: **选择**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n173: \n174: **理由**:\n175: - 遵循 Kubernetes API group 命名约定\n176: - `runtime` 表示运行时相关资源\n177: - `agentcube.volcano.sh` 表示 AgentCube 项目域名\n178: - `v1alpha1` 表示初始 API 版本\n179: \n180: ### 自动化代码生成\n181: \n182: **选择**: 使用 Makefile 自动化代码生成流程\n183: \n184: **理由**:\n185: - 标准化代码生成流程\n186: - 易于集成到 CI/CD\n187: - 确保代码与 CRD 定义同步\n188: \n189: **Makefile 示例**:\n190: ```makefile\n191: CODEGEN_PKG := $(shell go env GOPATH)/pkg/mod/k8s.io/code-generator@$(shell go list -m -f '{{.Version}}' k8s.io/code-generator)\n192: \n193: generate: codegen\n194: \t@echo \"Generation complete\"\n195: \n196: codegen:\n197: \t@echo \"Generating client code...\"\n198: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/client-gen/main.go \\\n199: \t\t--input-base=github.com/agentcube/apis \\\n200: \t\t--input=runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n201: \t\t--clientset-path=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client \\\n202: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\n203: \n204: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/informer-gen/main.go \\\n205: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n206: \t\t--versioned-clientset-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client/clientset/versioned \\\n207: \t\t--listers-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers \\\n208: \t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/informers \\\n209: \t\t--output-base=.\n210: \n211: \tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/lister-gen/main.go \\\n212: \t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n213: \t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers\n214: ```\n215: \n216: ## Alternatives Considered\n217: \n218: ### Alternative 1: 手动编写客户端代码\n219: \n220: **描述**: 手动编写所有客户端代码\n221: \n222: **优点**:\n223: - 完全控制代码实现\n224: - 可以自定义优化\n225: \n226: **缺点**:\n227: - 维护成本高\n228: - 容易出错\n229: - 难以与 CRD 定义同步\n230: - 违反 DRY 原则\n231: \n232: **选择**: 不采纳 - 使用 code-generator 自动生成\n233: \n234: ### Alternative 2: 使用其他代码生成工具\n235: \n236: **描述**: 使用 kubebuilder 或 operator-framework 的代码生成\n237: \n238: **优点**:\n239: - 与 Controller-Runtime 集成\n240: - 提供更多高级功能\n241: \n242: **缺点**:\n243: - 引入额外依赖\n244: - 可能过于重量级\n245: - 生成的代码可能不符合我们的需求\n246: \n247: **选择**: 不采纳 - 使用轻量级的 code-generator\n248: \n249: ### Alternative 3: 直接使用 REST API\n250: \n251: **描述**: 不生成类型化客户端，直接使用 REST API\n252: \n253: **优点**:\n254: - 无需生成代码\n255: - 语言无关\n256: \n257: **缺点**:\n258: - 缺乏类型安全\n259: - 开发效率低\n260: - 容易出错\n261: - 无法利用编译时检查\n262: \n263: **选择**: 不采纳 - 类型安全对 Go 项目至关重要\n264: \n265: ## Implementation Plan\n266: \n267: ### Phase 1: 项目初始化 (Day 1)\n268: \n269: 1. 创建 client-go 目录结构\n270: 2. 初始化 Go module\n271: 3. 配置 go.mod 依赖\n272: 4. 创建基础目录\n273: 5. 设置 Makefile\n274: \n275: **检查清单**:\n276: - [ ] 目录结构创建\n277: - [ ] Go module 初始化\n278: - [ ] 依赖配置\n279: - [ ] Makefile 创建\n280: \n281: ### Phase 2: API 类型定义 (Day 1-2)\n282: \n283: 1. 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录\n284: 2. 定义 doc.go\n285: 3. 定义 register.go\n286: 4. 定义 types.go\n287: 5. 定义 AgentRuntime 类型\n288: 6. 定义 CodeInterpreter 类型\n289: \n290: **检查清单**:\n291: - [ ] doc.go 创建\n292: - [ ] register.go 创建\n293: - [ ] types.go 创建\n294: - [ ] AgentRuntime 类型定义\n295: - [ ] CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n296: \n297: ### Phase 3: 代码生成配置 (Day 2)\n298: \n299: 1. 配置 code-generator 参数\n300: 2. 创建代码生成脚本\n301: 3. 配置 Makefile 目标\n302: 4. 测试代码生成\n303: \n304: **检查清单**:\n305: - [ ] code-generator 配置\n306: - [ ] 生成脚本创建\n307: - [ ] Makefile 目标配置\n308: - [ ] 代码生成测试\n309: \n310: ### Phase 4: ClientSet 生成 (Day 2-3)\n311: \n312: 1. 生成 clientset 代码\n313: 2. 验证生成的接口\n314: 3. 测试 CRUD 操作\n315: 4. 测试 namespace-scoped 操作\n316: \n317: **检查清单**:\n318: - [ ] clientset 生成\n319: - [ ] 接口验证\n320: - [ ] CRUD 测试\n321: - [ ] namespace 测试\n322: \n323: ### Phase 5: Informer 生成 (Day 3-4)\n324: \n325: 1. 生成 informer 代码\n326: 2. 实现 AgentRuntime informer\n327: 3. 实现 CodeInterpreter informer\n328: 4. 测试事件处理\n329: \n330: **检查清单**:\n331: - [ ] informer 生成\n332: - [ ] AgentRuntime informer\n333: - [ ] CodeInterpreter informer\n334: - [ ] 事件处理测试\n335: \n336: ### Phase 6: Lister 生成 (Day 4)\n337: \n338: 1. 生成 lister 代码\n339: 2. 实现 AgentRuntime lister\n340: 3. 实现 CodeInterpreter lister\n341: 4. 测试只读访问\n342: \n343: **检查清单**:\n344: - [ ] lister 生成\n345: - [ ] AgentRuntime lister\n346: - [ ] CodeInterpreter lister\n347: - [ ] 只读访问测试\n348: \n349: ### Phase 7: 测试和验证 (Day 4-5)\n350: \n351: 1. 编写单元测试\n352: 2. 编写集成测试\n353: 3. 测试所有 API 操作\n354: 4. 测试错误处理\n355: 5. 性能测试\n356: \n357: **检查清单**:\n358: - [ ] 单元测试\n359: - [ ] 集成测试\n360: - [ ] API 测试\n361: - [ ] 错误处理测试\n362: - [ ] 性能测试\n363: \n364: ### Phase 8: 文档和示例 (Day 5)\n365: \n366: 1. 编写 README.md\n367: 2. 编写 API 文档\n368: 3. 创建使用示例\n369: 4. 编写最佳实践指南\n370: \n371: **检查清单**:\n372: - [ ] README.md\n373: - [ ] API 文档\n374: - [ ] 使用示例\n375: - [ ] 最佳实践指南\n376: \n377: ### Phase 9: CI/CD 集成 (Day 5-6)\n378: \n379: 1. 配置 CI pipeline\n380: 2. 自动化代码生成\n381: 3. 自动化测试\n382: 4. 发布流程\n383: \n384: **检查清单**:\n385: - [ ] CI 配置\n386: - [ ] 自动化生成\n387: - [ ] 自动化测试\n388: - [ ] 发布流程\n389: \n390: ## Testing Strategy\n391: \n392: ### Unit Tests\n393: \n394: 1. **Client 测试**\n395:    - 测试 CRUD 操作\n396:    - 测试错误处理\n397:    - 测试参数验证\n398: \n399: 2. **Informer 测试**\n400:    - 测试事件触发\n401:    - 测试缓存更新\n402:    - 测试处理器注册\n403: \n404: 3. **Lister 测试**\n405:    - 测试资源查询\n406:    - 测试缓存命中\n407:    - 测试 namespace 过滤\n408: \n409: ### Integration Tests\n410: \n411: 1. **ClientSet 集成测试**\n412:    - 连接真实 Kubernetes 集群\n413:    - 测试完整 CRUD 流程\n414:    - 测试并发操作\n415: \n416: 2. **Informer 集成测试**\n417:    - 测试实时事件监听\n418:    - 测试多客户端同步\n419:    - 测试重连机制\n420: \n421: 3. **Lister 集成测试**\n422:    - 测试大规模资源查询\n423:    - 测试缓存一致性\n424:    - 测试性能指标\n425: \n426: ### End-to-End Tests\n427: \n428: 1. **完整工作流测试**\n429:    - 创建资源\n430:    - Watch 资源变更\n431:    - 更新资源\n432:    - 删除资源\n433: \n434: 2. **错误恢复测试**\n435:    - 测试网络故障\n436:    - 测试 API 服务器故障\n437:    - 测试重连机制\n438: \n439: 3. **性能测试**\n440:    - 测试高并发场景\n441:    - 测试大规模资源操作\n442:    - 测试内存使用\n443: \n444: ## API Specification\n445: \n446: ### AgentRuntime Client API\n447: \n448: ```go\n449: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n450:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n451:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n452:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n453:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n454:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n455:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n456:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n457:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n458:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n459: }\n460: ```\n461: \n462: ### CodeInterpreter Client API\n463: \n464: ```go\n465: type CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n466:     Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n467:     Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n468:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n469:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n470:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n471:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n472:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n473:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n474:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n475: }\n476: ```\n477: \n478: ## Configuration\n479: \n480: ### Go Module 配置\n481: \n482: ```go\n483: module github.com/agentcube/client-go\n484: \n485: go 1.19\n486: \n487: require (\n488:     k8s.io/api v0.26.0\n489:     k8s.io/apimachinery v0.26.0\n490:     k8s.io/client-go v0.26.0\n491:     k8s.io/code-generator v0.26.0\n492: )\n493: ```\n494: \n495: ## Security Considerations\n496: \n497: 1. **身份验证**\n498:    - 支持 kubeconfig 配置\n499:    - 支持 ServiceAccount token\n500:    - 支持 TLS 证书\n501: \n502: 2. **授权**\n503:    - 遵循 Kubernetes RBAC\n504:    - 权限检查\n505:    - 审计日志\n506: \n507: 3. **数据安全**\n508:    - 敏感数据加密\n509:    - 安全的日志记录\n510:    - 错误信息脱敏\n511: \n512: ## Performance Considerations\n513: \n514: 1. **缓存策略**\n515:    - Informer 本地缓存\n516:    - 高效的缓存更新\n517:    - 缓存一致性保证\n518: \n519: 2. **并发控制**\n520:    - 连接池管理\n521:    - 请求限流\n522:    - 并发安全\n523: \n524: 3. **资源使用**\n525:    - 内存优化\n526:    - Goroutine 管理\n527:    - 连接复用\n528: \n529: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n530: \n531: ### 关键指标\n532: \n533: 1. **客户端指标**\n534:    - API 调用延迟\n535:    - API 调用成功率\n536:    - API 调用频率\n537: \n538: 2. **Informer 指标**\n539:    - 事件处理延迟\n540:    - 缓存命中率\n541:    - 同步状态\n542: \n543: 3. **Lister 指标**\n544:    - 查询延迟\n545:    - 缓存大小\n546:    - 查询频率\n547: \n548: ## Success Criteria\n549: \n550: - 成功生成完整的 client-go 客户端库\n551: - 所有 CRUD 操作正常工作\n552: - Informer 和 Lister 功能完善\n553: - 测试覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n554: - 文档完整清晰\n555: - 示例代码可用\n556: - CI/CD 集成完成\n557: \n558: ## References\n559: \n560: - [Kubernetes client-go Documentation](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go)\n561: - [Kubernetes code-generator](https://github.com/kubernetes/code-generator)\n562: - [AgentCube Spec](../../spec.md)\n563: - [AR-035 Spec](./spec.md)\n564: - [Kubernetes API Conventions](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md)\n\n(End of file - total 564 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Overview\n\n为 AgentCube 平台生成基于 Kubernetes client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供对自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）的强类型 API 访问能力，支持 CRUD 操作、Watch 机制和 Informer 模式。\n\n## Purpose\n\nclient-go 类型客户端是 AgentCube 平台开发者工具链的核心组成部分，旨在：\n\n1. **类型安全** - 提供编译时类型检查，避免运行时错误\n2. **开发效率** - 简化 Kubernetes API 调用，提供简洁的开发体验\n3. **标准化接口** - 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 最佳实践和约定\n4. **高性能** - 支持高效的 Watch 和 Informer 机制\n5. **可维护性** - 自动生成客户端代码，与 CRD 定义保持同步\n\n## Module\n\n`client-go` - Go 客户端库\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775893008481,"end":1775893008503}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893008507,"sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","part":{"id":"prt_d7b78cb57001hkYhwHMHqDK7M1","messageID":"msg_d7b78b9a2001VtshnlnNcV94uQ","sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-502de33be94d4696b43521b25e0fe78f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/router/handlers.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/router/handlers.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package router\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"net/http\"\n5: \n6: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n7: \t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n8: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n9: \n10: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n11: )\n12: \n13: type Handler struct {\n14: \tsessionManager SessionManager\n15: \tjwtManager     *JWTManager\n16: \treverseProxy   *ReverseProxy\n17: }\n18: \n19: func NewHandler(sessionManager SessionManager, jwtManager *JWTManager, reverseProxy *ReverseProxy) *Handler {\n20: \treturn &Handler{\n21: \t\tsessionManager: sessionManager,\n22: \t\tjwtManager:     jwtManager,\n23: \t\treverseProxy:   reverseProxy,\n24: \t}\n25: }\n26: \n27: func (h *Handler) handleHealthLive(c *gin.Context) {\n28: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{\n29: \t\t\"status\": \"alive\",\n30: \t})\n31: }\n32: \n33: func (h *Handler) handleHealthReady(c *gin.Context) {\n34: \tif h.sessionManager == nil {\n35: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusServiceUnavailable, NewErrorResponse(\n36: \t\t\t\"session manager not available\",\n37: \t\t\tErrSessionManagerNotReady,\n38: \t\t))\n39: \t\treturn\n40: \t}\n41: \n42: \tif h.jwtManager == nil {\n43: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusServiceUnavailable, NewErrorResponse(\n44: \t\t\t\"JWT manager not available\",\n45: \t\t\t\"JWT_MANAGER_NOT_READY\",\n46: \t\t))\n47: \t\treturn\n48: \t}\n49: \n50: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{\n51: \t\t\"status\": \"ready\",\n52: \t})\n53: }\n54: \n55: func (h *Handler) handleAgentInvoke(c *gin.Context) {\n56: \th.handleInvocation(c, types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n57: }\n58: \n59: func (h *Handler) handleCodeInterpreterInvoke(c *gin.Context) {\n60: \th.handleInvocation(c, types.CodeInterpreterKind)\n61: }\n62: \n63: func (h *Handler) handleInvocation(c *gin.Context, kind string) {\n64: \tnamespace := c.Param(\"namespace\")\n65: \tname := c.Param(\"name\")\n66: \tpath := c.Param(\"path\")\n67: \n68: \tif !isValidNamespace(namespace) {\n69: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n70: \t\t\t\"invalid namespace format\",\n71: \t\t\tGetErrorCode(&ValidationError{Field: \"namespace\"}),\n72: \t\t))\n73: \t\treturn\n74: \t}\n75: \n76: \tif !isValidResourceName(name) {\n77: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n78: \t\t\t\"invalid resource name format\",\n79: \t\t\tGetErrorCode(&ValidationError{Field: \"name\"}),\n80: \t\t))\n81: \t\treturn\n82: \t}\n83: \n84: \tsessionID := h.extractSessionID(c)\n85: \n86: \tsandboxInfo, err := h.sessionManager.GetSandboxBySession(c.Request.Context(), sessionID, namespace, name, kind)\n87: \tif err != nil {\n88: \t\tif _, ok := err.(*SandboxNotFoundError); ok {\n89: \t\t\tsessionID, sandboxInfo, err = h.sessionManager.CreateSession(c.Request.Context(), name, namespace, kind)\n90: \t\t\tif err != nil {\n91: \t\t\t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to create session: %v\", err)\n92: \t\t\t\tc.JSON(GetHTTPStatusCode(err), NewErrorResponse(err.Error(), GetErrorCode(err)))\n93: \t\t\t\treturn\n94: \t\t\t}\n95: \t\t} else {\n96: \t\t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to get sandbox: %v\", err)\n97: \t\t\tc.JSON(GetHTTPStatusCode(err), NewErrorResponse(err.Error(), GetErrorCode(err)))\n98: \t\t\treturn\n99: \t\t}\n100: \t}\n101: \n102: \tif path != \"\" {\n103: \t\tc.Request.URL.Path = \"/\" + path\n104: \t}\n105: \n106: \tc.Header(\"X-Agentcube-Session-ID\", sessionID)\n107: \tc.Request.URL.Path = sanitizePath(c.Request.URL.Path)\n108: \n109: \th.reverseProxy.ServeHTTP(c.Writer, c.Request, sandboxInfo)\n110: }\n111: \n112: func (h *Handler) extractSessionID(c *gin.Context) string {\n113: \tsessionID := c.GetHeader(\"X-Agentcube-Session-ID\")\n114: \tif sessionID != \"\" {\n115: \t\tif err := parseSessionID(sessionID); err == nil {\n116: \t\t\treturn sessionID\n117: \t\t}\n118: \t}\n119: \n120: \treturn uuid.New().String()\n121: }\n122: \n123: func (h *Handler) generateSessionID() string {\n124: \treturn uuid.New().String()\n125: }\n126: \n127: func (h *Handler) handleCreateSession(c *gin.Context) {\n128: \tkind := c.Param(\"kind\")\n129: \tnamespace := c.Param(\"namespace\")\n130: \tname := c.Param(\"name\")\n131: \n132: \tif kind != \"agent-runtimes\" && kind != \"code-interpreters\" {\n133: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n134: \t\t\t\"invalid kind, must be agent-runtimes or code-interpreters\",\n135: \t\t\t\"INVALID_KIND\",\n136: \t\t))\n137: \t\treturn\n138: \t}\n139: \n140: \tkindType := types.AgentRuntimeKind\n141: \tif kind == \"code-interpreters\" {\n142: \t\tkindType = types.CodeInterpreterKind\n143: \t}\n144: \n145: \tif !isValidNamespace(namespace) {\n146: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n147: \t\t\t\"invalid namespace format\",\n148: \t\t\t\"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n149: \t\t))\n150: \t\treturn\n151: \t}\n152: \n153: \tif !isValidResourceName(name) {\n154: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n155: \t\t\t\"invalid resource name format\",\n156: \t\t\t\"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n157: \t\t))\n158: \t\treturn\n159: \t}\n160: \n161: \tsessionID, sandboxInfo, err := h.sessionManager.CreateSession(c.Request.Context(), name, namespace, kindType)\n162: \tif err != nil {\n163: \t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to create session: %v\", err)\n164: \t\tc.JSON(GetHTTPStatusCode(err), NewErrorResponse(err.Error(), GetErrorCode(err)))\n165: \t\treturn\n166: \t}\n167: \n168: \ttoken, err := h.jwtManager.GenerateToken(sessionID)\n169: \tif err != nil {\n170: \t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to generate JWT token: %v\", err)\n171: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, NewErrorResponse(\n172: \t\t\t\"failed to generate authentication token\",\n173: \t\t\t\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\",\n174: \t\t))\n175: \t\treturn\n176: \t}\n177: \n178: \tresponse := &CreateSessionResponse{\n179: \t\tSessionID:   sessionID,\n180: \t\tSandboxID:   sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n181: \t\tSandboxName: sandboxInfo.SandboxName,\n182: \t\tToken:       token,\n183: \t\tEntryPoints: sandboxInfo.EntryPoints,\n184: \t}\n185: \n186: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, response)\n187: }\n188: \n189: func (h *Handler) handleGetSession(c *gin.Context) {\n190: \tsessionID := c.Param(\"sessionID\")\n191: \n192: \tif sessionID == \"\" {\n193: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, NewErrorResponse(\n194: \t\t\t\"session ID is required\",\n195: \t\t\t\"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n196: \t\t))\n197: \t\treturn\n198: \t}\n199: \n200: \tsessions, err := h.sessionManager.ListSessions(c.Request.Context())\n201: \tif err != nil {\n202: \t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to list sessions: %v\", err)\n203: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, NewErrorResponse(\n204: \t\t\t\"failed to retrieve sessions\",\n205: \t\t\t\"INTERNAL_ERROR\",\n206: \t\t))\n207: \t\treturn\n208: \t}\n209: \n210: \tfor _, session := range sessions {\n211: \t\tif session.SessionID == sessionID {\n212: \t\t\tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, session)\n213: \t\t\treturn\n214: \t\t}\n215: \t}\n216: \n217: \tc.JSON(http.StatusNotFound, NewErrorResponse(\n218: \t\t\"session not found\",\n219: \t\t\"SESSION_NOT_FOUND\",\n220: \t))\n221: }\n\n(End of file - total 221 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package router\n\nimport (\n\t\"net/http\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n\t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n)\n\ntype Handler struct {\n\tsessionManager SessionManager\n\tjwtManager     *JWTManager\n\treverseProxy   *ReverseProxy\n}\n\nfunc NewHandler(sessionManager SessionManager, jwtManager *JWTManager, reverseProxy *ReverseProxy) *Handler {\n\treturn &Handler{","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/router/handlers.go","time":{"start":1775893008483,"end":1775893008505}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893008508,"sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","part":{"id":"prt_d7b78d047001OBPurb7ccEjxlS","messageID":"msg_d7b78b9a2001VtshnlnNcV94uQ","sessionID":"ses_284876bc8ffeO9xqS1ZVUVIIZd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7397f8caea344eb897c570cf44b5a863","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/picod/handlers.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/picod/handlers.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package picod\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"encoding/base64\"\n6: \t\"fmt\"\n7: \t\"io\"\n8: \t\"mime\"\n9: \t\"net/http\"\n10: \t\"os\"\n11: \t\"os/exec\"\n12: \t\"path/filepath\"\n13: \t\"strings\"\n14: \t\"time\"\n15: \n16: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n17: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n18: )\n19: \n20: func (s *Server) ExecuteHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n21: \tvar req ExecuteRequest\n22: \tif err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n23: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrInvalidCommand, \"invalid request body\", err.Error(), err))\n24: \t\treturn\n25: \t}\n26: \n27: \tif len(req.Command) == 0 {\n28: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrEmptyCommand, ErrMsgEmptyCommand, \"\", nil))\n29: \t\treturn\n30: \t}\n31: \n32: \ttimeout := DefaultTimeout\n33: \tif req.Timeout != \"\" {\n34: \t\tparsedTimeout, err := time.ParseDuration(req.Timeout)\n35: \t\tif err != nil {\n36: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrInvalidTimeout, \"invalid timeout format\", err.Error(), err))\n37: \t\t\treturn\n38: \t\t}\n39: \t\ttimeout = parsedTimeout\n40: \t}\n41: \n42: \tworkingDir := s.workspaceDir\n43: \tif req.WorkingDir != \"\" {\n44: \t\tsanitizedDir, err := s.sanitizePath(req.WorkingDir)\n45: \t\tif err != nil {\n46: \t\t\tHandleError(c, err)\n47: \t\t\treturn\n48: \t\t}\n49: \t\tworkingDir = sanitizedDir\n50: \t}\n51: \n52: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), timeout)\n53: \tdefer cancel()\n54: \n55: \tcmd := exec.CommandContext(ctx, req.Command[0], req.Command[1:]...)\n56: \tcmd.Dir = workingDir\n57: \n58: \tenv := os.Environ()\n59: \tfor k, v := range req.Env {\n60: \t\tenv = append(env, fmt.Sprintf(\"%s=%s\", k, v))\n61: \t}\n62: \tcmd.Env = env\n63: \n64: \tstartTime := time.Now()\n65: \tstdout, err := cmd.CombinedOutput()\n66: \tendTime := time.Now()\n67: \tduration := endTime.Sub(startTime)\n68: \n69: \texitCode := 0\n70: \tif err != nil {\n71: \t\tif ctx.Err() == context.DeadlineExceeded {\n72: \t\t\texitCode = TimeoutExitCode\n73: \t\t} else {\n74: \t\t\tif exitError, ok := err.(*exec.ExitError); ok {\n75: \t\t\t\texitCode = exitError.ExitCode()\n76: \t\t\t} else {\n77: \t\t\t\texitCode = 1\n78: \t\t\t}\n79: \t\t}\n80: \t}\n81: \n82: \tresponse := ExecuteResponse{\n83: \t\tStdout:    string(stdout),\n84: \t\tStderr:    \"\",\n85: \t\tExitCode:  exitCode,\n86: \t\tDuration:  duration.Seconds(),\n87: \t\tStartTime: startTime.UTC(),\n88: \t\tEndTime:   endTime.UTC(),\n89: \t}\n90: \n91: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, response)\n92: }\n93: \n94: func (s *Server) UploadFileHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n95: \tcontentType := c.GetHeader(HeaderContentType)\n96: \n97: \tif strings.HasPrefix(contentType, MIMEMultipart) {\n98: \t\tif err := c.Request.ParseMultipartForm(32 << 20); err != nil {\n99: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrInvalidCommand, \"failed to parse multipart form\", err.Error(), err))\n100: \t\t\treturn\n101: \t\t}\n102: \n103: \t\tpath := c.PostForm(\"path\")\n104: \t\tfile, header, err := c.Request.FormFile(\"file\")\n105: \t\tif err != nil {\n106: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrMissingPath, \"path or file form field missing\", \"\", err))\n107: \t\t\treturn\n108: \t\t}\n109: \t\tdefer file.Close()\n110: \n111: \t\tif path == \"\" {\n112: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrMissingPath, \"path form field missing\", \"\", nil))\n113: \t\t\treturn\n114: \t\t}\n115: \n116: \t\tmodeStr := c.PostForm(\"mode\")\n117: \t\tmode := parseFileMode(modeStr)\n118: \n119: \t\tsanitizedPath, err := s.sanitizePath(path)\n120: \t\tif err != nil {\n121: \t\t\tHandleError(c, err)\n122: \t\t\treturn\n123: \t\t}\n124: \n125: \t\tif err := os.MkdirAll(filepath.Dir(sanitizedPath), DefaultDirMode); err != nil {\n126: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to create directory\", err.Error(), err))\n127: \t\t\treturn\n128: \t\t}\n129: \n130: \t\tdst, err := os.OpenFile(sanitizedPath, os.O_WRONLY|os.O_CREATE|os.O_TRUNC, mode)\n131: \t\tif err != nil {\n132: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to create file\", err.Error(), err))\n133: \t\t\treturn\n134: \t\t}\n135: \t\tdefer dst.Close()\n136: \n137: \t\tif _, err := io.Copy(dst, file); err != nil {\n138: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to write file\", err.Error(), err))\n139: \t\t\treturn\n140: \t\t}\n141: \n142: \t\tklog.Infof(\"Uploaded file: %s (size: %d, original: %s)\", sanitizedPath, header.Size, header.Filename)\n143: \n144: \t\tfileInfo, err := s.getFileInfo(sanitizedPath)\n145: \t\tif err != nil {\n146: \t\t\tHandleError(c, err)\n147: \t\t\treturn\n148: \t\t}\n149: \n150: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, fileInfo)\n151: \t} else {\n152: \t\tvar req UploadFileRequest\n153: \t\tif err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n154: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrInvalidCommand, \"invalid request body\", err.Error(), err))\n155: \t\t\treturn\n156: \t\t}\n157: \n158: \t\tcontent, err := base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString(req.Content)\n159: \t\tif err != nil {\n160: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrInvalidBase64, ErrMsgInvalidBase64, err.Error(), err))\n161: \t\t\treturn\n162: \t\t}\n163: \n164: \t\tsanitizedPath, err := s.sanitizePath(req.Path)\n165: \t\tif err != nil {\n166: \t\t\tHandleError(c, err)\n167: \t\t\treturn\n168: \t\t}\n169: \n170: \t\tif err := os.MkdirAll(filepath.Dir(sanitizedPath), DefaultDirMode); err != nil {\n171: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to create directory\", err.Error(), err))\n172: \t\t\treturn\n173: \t\t}\n174: \n175: \t\tmode := parseFileMode(req.Mode)\n176: \t\tif err := os.WriteFile(sanitizedPath, content, mode); err != nil {\n177: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to write file\", err.Error(), err))\n178: \t\t\treturn\n179: \t\t}\n180: \n181: \t\tklog.Infof(\"Uploaded file: %s (size: %d)\", sanitizedPath, len(content))\n182: \n183: \t\tfileInfo, err := s.getFileInfo(sanitizedPath)\n184: \t\tif err != nil {\n185: \t\t\tHandleError(c, err)\n186: \t\t\treturn\n187: \t\t}\n188: \n189: \t\tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, fileInfo)\n190: \t}\n191: }\n192: \n193: func (s *Server) ListFilesHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n194: \tpath := c.Query(\"path\")\n195: \tif path == \"\" {\n196: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrMissingPath, ErrMsgMissingPathParam, \"\", nil))\n197: \t\treturn\n198: \t}\n199: \n200: \tsanitizedPath, err := s.sanitizePath(path)\n201: \tif err != nil {\n202: \t\tHandleError(c, err)\n203: \t\treturn\n204: \t}\n205: \n206: \tentries, err := os.ReadDir(sanitizedPath)\n207: \tif err != nil {\n208: \t\tif os.IsNotExist(err) {\n209: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrDirectoryNotFound, ErrMsgDirectoryNotFound, \"\", err))\n210: \t\t} else {\n211: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to read directory\", err.Error(), err))\n212: \t\t}\n213: \t\treturn\n214: \t}\n215: \n216: \tvar files []FileEntry\n217: \tfor _, entry := range entries {\n218: \t\tinfo, err := entry.Info()\n219: \t\tif err != nil {\n220: \t\t\tklog.Warningf(\"Failed to get info for %s: %v\", entry.Name(), err)\n221: \t\t\tcontinue\n222: \t\t}\n223: \n224: \t\tfiles = append(files, FileEntry{\n225: \t\t\tName:     entry.Name(),\n226: \t\t\tSize:     info.Size(),\n227: \t\t\tModified: info.ModTime(),\n228: \t\t\tMode:     fmt.Sprintf(\"%04o\", info.Mode().Perm()),\n229: \t\t\tIsDir:    entry.IsDir(),\n230: \t\t})\n231: \t}\n232: \n233: \tresponse := ListFilesResponse{\n234: \t\tFiles: files,\n235: \t}\n236: \n237: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, response)\n238: }\n239: \n240: func (s *Server) DownloadFileHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n241: \tpath := c.Param(\"path\")\n242: \tif path == \"\" {\n243: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrMissingPath, ErrMsgMissingPathParam, \"\", nil))\n244: \t\treturn\n245: \t}\n246: \n247: \tpath = strings.TrimPrefix(path, \"/\")\n248: \n249: \tsanitizedPath, err := s.sanitizePath(path)\n250: \tif err != nil {\n251: \t\tHandleError(c, err)\n252: \t\treturn\n253: \t}\n254: \n255: \tinfo, err := os.Stat(sanitizedPath)\n256: \tif err != nil {\n257: \t\tif os.IsNotExist(err) {\n258: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrFileNotFound, ErrMsgFileNotFound, \"\", err))\n259: \t\t} else {\n260: \t\t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to get file info\", err.Error(), err))\n261: \t\t}\n262: \t\treturn\n263: \t}\n264: \n265: \tif info.IsDir() {\n266: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrPathIsDirectory, ErrMsgPathIsDirectory, \"\", nil))\n267: \t\treturn\n268: \t}\n269: \n270: \tcontent, err := os.ReadFile(sanitizedPath)\n271: \tif err != nil {\n272: \t\tHandleError(c, NewError(ErrServerInternal, \"failed to read file\", err.Error(), err))\n273: \t\treturn\n274: \t}\n275: \n276: \tc.Header(HeaderContentDescription, \"File Transfer\")\n277: \tc.Header(HeaderContentEncoding, \"binary\")\n278: \tc.Header(HeaderContentDisposition, fmt.Sprintf(\"attachment; filename=\\\"%s\\\"\", filepath.Base(sanitizedPath)))\n279: \n280: \tmimeType := mime.TypeByExtension(filepath.Ext(sanitizedPath))\n281: \tif mimeType == \"\" {\n282: \t\tmimeType = MIMEOctetStream\n283: \t}\n284: \tc.Header(HeaderContentType, mimeType)\n285: \n286: \tc.Data(http.StatusOK, mimeType, content)\n287: }\n288: \n289: func (s *Server) HealthCheckHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n290: \tuptime := time.Since(s.startTime)\n291: \n292: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{\n293: \t\t\"status\":  \"ok\",\n294: \t\t\"service\": ServiceName,\n295: \t\t\"version\": Version,\n296: \t\t\"uptime\":  uptime.String(),\n297: \t})\n298: }\n\n(End of file - total 298 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package picod\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"encoding/base64\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"io\"\n\t\"mime\"\n\t\"net/http\"\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"os/exec\"\n\t\"path/filepath\"\n\t\"strings\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\nfunc (s *Server) ExecuteHandler(c *gin.Context) {","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/picod/handlers.go","time":{"start":1775893008487,"end":1775893008507}}}}
